177 A.3d 119 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. ROBERT RUCKER, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-417 September Term 2017

079670 December 8, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003295-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

*542It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
